rol Charts]])<ref>{{cite web|title= Top 100 Single-Jahrescharts \u2013 1980 |publisher= Offiziellecharts.de. [[GfK Entertainment]] |url= https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/single-jahr/for-date-1980 |archivedate= 8 May 2015 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150508235748/https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/single-jahr/for-date-1980 |language= de}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|43\n|-\n|Italy ([[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])<ref name=\"Italy\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|}\n\n===Sales and certifications===\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=France|type=single|artist=Buggles|title=Video Killed the Radio Star|award=Platinum|certyear=1979 |recent=false|salesamount=1,212,000|salesref=<ref>{{cite web|title= Les Singles de Platine |website= InfoDisc |accessdate= 5 June 2012 |url= http://www.infodisc.fr/S_Certif_Platine.php?debut=21 |language= fr |url-status= dead |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140428071242/http://www.infodisc.fr/S_Certif_Platine.php?debut=21 |archivedate= 28 April 2014}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Spain|type=single|artist=Buggles|title=Video Killed the Radio Star|relyear=1979|award=Gold|salesamount=50,000|certref=<ref>{{cite book|first= Fernando |last= Salaverri |title= S\u00f3lo \u00e9xitos: a\u00f1o a a\u00f1o, 1959\u20132002 |edition= 1st |date= September 2005 |publisher= Fundaci\u00f3n Autor-SGAE |location= Spain |url= http://www.mediafire.com/view/x263f6daopkswo8 |isbn= 84-8048-639-2 |language= es}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|type=single|artist=Buggles|title=Video Killed the Radio Star|award=Gold|relyear=1979 |certyear=1979}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Accolades==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!scope=\"col\"|Publication/TV Show/Author(s)\n!scope=\"col\"|Country\n!scope=\"col\"|Accolade\n!scope=\"col\"|Year\n!scope=\"col\"|Rank\n|-\n|scope=\"row\"|''[[20 to 1]]''\n|Australia\n|Top 20 One Hit Wonders<ref>{{cite episode|titl